Package: campfin
Type: Package
Title: Help Wrangle Campaign Finance Data
Version: 0.0.0.9024
Authors@R: as.person(c("Kiernan Nicholls <kiernann@protonmail.com> [aut, cre]"))
Description: This package was created for use by the Accountability Project team 
    at the Investigative Reporting Workshop. The Accountability Project 
    standardizes and disambiguates campaign finance data to make it more 
    searchable. The functions included facilitate the exploration and wrangling
    of data, with an emphasis on string normalization.
